# Data Absorber Student

A student productivity platform designed to help students organize notes, documents, assignments, and academic resources in one place.

## Features

- Subject Management
- Notes Management
- PDF Uploads
- Assignment Tracking
- Calendar Events

## Tech Stack

- Python
- FastAPI
- SQLite
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

## Roadmap

- AI Study Assistant
- Flashcards
- Quiz Generator
- Student Collaboration
- Note Sharing
